{"lemma":"صُبَّيْرِ","slug":"صُبَّيْرِ","root":"ص.ب.ر","root_slug":"ص-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ب-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23680"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23680","headword_ar":"صَبِيرٌ","root":"Sbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAbirN","text_ar":"صَابِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A surety."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa bihi SabiyrN","text_ar":"هُوَ بِهِ صَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is a surety for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabiyru qawomK","text_ar":"صَبِيرُ قَوْمٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The chief, head, director, conductor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manager, of the affairs of a people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he who is patient for, and with, a people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, in"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the managing of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their affairs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubaraA='u","text_ar":"صُبَرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) ―         -b4-  [And accord. to Golius,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A solitary man, having neither offspring nor brother:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but app. a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SunobuwrN","text_ar":"صُنْبُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is thus expl. in the S in this art.]       -A2-  Also, (S, M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubaArapN","text_ar":"صُبَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A white cloud;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiborN","text_ar":"صِبْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuborN","text_ar":"صُبْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaArN","text_ar":"اَصْبَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white clouds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaAnN","text_ar":"اَصْبَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiborN","text_ar":"صِبْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuborN","text_ar":"صُبْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, Yaakoob, S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white clouds that scarcely ever,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"never, give rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white clouds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that become disposed one above another"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the manner of steps:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dense cloud that is above another cloud:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stationary portion of cloud:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion of cloud which one sees as though it were"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSobuwrap","text_ar":"مَصْبُورَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detained;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this explanation is of weak authority: or, accord. to AHn,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds remaining stationary a day and a night;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though detained: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds in which are blackness and whiteness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds slow in motion, by reason of their heaviness and the abundance of their water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 786:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiyrN","text_ar":"صَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the same as the sing., (M,) or it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuburN","text_ar":"صُبُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, M, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiyrN","text_ar":"صَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~abiyru","text_ar":"الصَّبِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the name of a particular mountain. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [And accord. to Freytag, as from the K, in which I do not find this meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hill consisting of stones."},{"kind":"text","text":"]       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiyrN","text_ar":"صَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) i. e. (TA) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabiyr","text_ar":"صَبِير"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaAn","text_ar":"خَوَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or table, or thing upon which one eats], (M, A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thin, round cake of bread, which is spread beneath the food that one eats:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, K:) or (K, TA, but in the CK “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which the food to be eaten at a wedding-feast is ladled"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the maker of the bread:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) also called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiyrapN","text_ar":"صَبِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","A","S","As","O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}